text: No. 6 Collaborations Project is the fourth studio album by Ed Sheeran. It was released on 12 July 2019. The reason this album was created was because of one of his EPs that was named No.5 Collaborations. There are 15 songs on this album. And this album was just collaborations with other artist. Hits include I Don't Care, Beautiful People and South of the Border. Category:2019 albums Category:Ed Sheeran albums
title: No. 6 Collaborations Project
